(152, 'Yudi', '', 'Xue', '', 'yudi.xue@usask.ca', '<p>I am a M.Sc student in the Interaction Lab under the co-supervision of <a href="http://www.cs.usask.ca/~gutwin/">Dr Carl Gutwin</a> and <a href="http://www.cs.usask.ca/~osgood">Dr Nate Osgood</a>. My research is focused on supporting asynchronous workspace awareness in simulation modeling collaboration. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nMy interests:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Information Visualization</li>\r\n<li>Software Engineering</li>\r\n<li>Social/Group Awareness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\nProject(s):\r\n<p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/uofs-silver-hg/">SILVER</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://friend-viz.appspot.com/">Friend-Viz</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://gephi.org/2011/the-gsoc-rocket-launched-2/">Google Summer of Code 2011</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<a href="http://ca.linkedin.com/in/yudixue">\r\n      \r\n          <img src="http://www.linkedin.com/img/webpromo/btn_viewmy_160x33.png" width="160" height="33" border="0" alt="View Yudi Xue''s profile on LinkedIn">\r\n        \r\n    </a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<a href="http://www.', 'alumni', 'yux577', NULL, NULL),
